headline: General Mills (GIS) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: General Mills (GIS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 14.75% and 1.61%, respectively, for the quarter ended November 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
